#: lib/options.h:48
msgid "View program:"
msgstr "檢視程式："

#: lib/options.h:49
msgid ""
"The default program used to view files. If this is blank, the internal file "
"viewer will be used"
msgstr "預設用來查看檔案的程式。如果本設定值留空，則使用內建的檔案檢視程式"

#: lib/options.h:51
msgid "Edit program:"
msgstr "編輯程式："

